@node "ToolTypes" "ToolTypes"
@next "ToolTypes"
@prev "ToolTypes"

@{JCENTER}@{b}@{u}ToolTypes@{ub}@{uu}
@{JLEFT}
 Window2Front has just a few of tooltypes:

 @{b}HOTKEY@{ub}: Set a hotkey for next window. Default = CTRL Y
 @{b}REV_HOTKEY@{ub}: Set a hotkey for previous window. Default = CTRL SHIFT Y
 @{b}CX_PRIORITY@{ub}: Sets the priority.

@endnode

